{"tid":802323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】胃病男危坐升降機橋塔 消防警方大陣仗戒備","createTime":"2018-09-01T11:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T16:56:47.000Z","uid":50162,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29e92301550aaece70e1d6e272b7d882c945ad32","tid":802323,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"今早(1日)11時05分，一名戴鴨舌帽、穿白衫及黑褲的姓魏(72歲)男子，被發現在秀茂坪安泰邨對出、通往順安道的升降機橋塔第13層梯間，用櫈爬上欄杆後，面向梯間背向街外危坐，有女途人見狀報警。消防到場在橋塔底張開救生氣墊，另一批消防員則在14層梯間戒備，「飛將軍」準備隨時救人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，魏翁因不堪胃病折騰尋死，警方派出4男4女談判專家輪流向其游說，同時通知他的家人到場勸說，惜事主不為所動。期間，魏翁一度在欄杆攀爬，情況險象環生。由於現場天氣惡劣，橫風橫雨，目擊街坊也替事主「好牙煙」。由於警方封閉橋塔，令安泰邨居民不能經該處出入，不少街坊駐足圍觀，議論紛紛。消防同時出動高空拯救專隊及攀山拯救專隊到場救援。<br />\n<br />\n事件擾攘至今午約2時20分，魏翁開始出現疲倦，身體不停晃動，消防恐他墮樓，遂一擁而上合力將他拉住，將他帶返安全位置，其後由救護車送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=71119484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n危坐欄杆事主一度攀爬，險象環生。(陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=290f3dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方及消防正展開拯救。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=a82a588b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主（箭嘴示）危坐升降機橋塔欄杆。(梁志雄攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=99326ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防將危坐事主拉回安全位置。(陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_05b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=18170adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防攀山拯救專隊到場。(陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_06b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=4009a3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲救事主送院。(陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/photo/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_07b.jpg?20180901164809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20180901164809&h=c12cc6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防曾張開救生氣墊戒備。(陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2Fbkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001.html&d=3KUophfEX40xhIzkkEJMkqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3f837053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180901/bkn-20180901120310497-0901_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n＃安泰邪邨 ＃前石礦場 ＃死亡勝地 ＃最賤公屋"},{"pid":"5217a8664099fdd7f247046a27be820d292304ab","tid":802323,"uid":57410,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"其實跳樓自殺黎講  實際上應該一跳就跳到<br />\n<br />\n點解佢既過程咁耐？ 耐到消防員開埋都仲未跳<br />\n<br />\n搞咩？"},{"pid":"06579cc556a0554f544d2e0a959084bcb046b7b9","tid":802323,"uid":50162,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5217a8664099fdd7f247046a27be820d292304ab","tid":802323,"uid":57410,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"其實跳樓自殺黎講  實際上應該一跳就跳到<br />\n<br />\n點解佢既過程咁耐？ 耐到消防員開埋都仲未跳<br />\n<br />\n搞咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"決心不足"},{"pid":"78f18d26c033e16bb6811114a1985f593de17598","tid":802323,"uid":182286,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fce3f4476dc8eecdd1f8e9acc3cde4d5b4d9550","tid":802323,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"網上行堅守崗位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b39bf7dd8a8cb5069c7b7174df88570bab5e33","tid":802323,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"跳樓失敗"},{"pid":"2b5a9dcdde3f6a5b70e620f950776988673fef4d","tid":802323,"uid":155523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"真心唔明點解安達邨無呢d跳樓人士<br />\n次次新聞都係安泰邨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經俾新樓你啦 仲跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd5e7bbb6679377948e178ff2ee430eb933c69","tid":802323,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"死廢老跳樓都冇決心。"},{"pid":"c3f40994979807c1f1cde42a555fa05e335e4f6a","tid":802323,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"因乜解究巴打你對安